com.moniuliuma.fingerprint

Interface Importer

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ImporterImpl

    public interface Importer
    Importer allows to import images and FMDs in binary form, from existing data.

      • ImportRaw

              int width,
              int height,
              int dpi,
              int finger_position,
              int cbeff_id,
              Fid.Format out_format,
              int out_dpi,
              boolean rotate180)
       throws DeviceException
        Imports raw image and converts it to ANSI or ISO format.
        Parameters:
        data - - Image data to import.
        width - - Width of the image.
        height - - Height of the image.
        dpi - - Resolution of the image in DPI.
        finger_position - - Position of the finger.
        cbeff_id - - CBEFF product ID, from IBIA registry.
        out_format - - Format of the resulting FID.
        out_dpi - - Resolution of the resulting FID in DPI.
        rotate180 - - flag: rotate image, false - do not rotate, true - rotate.
        Returns:
        Imported FID
        Throws:
        DeviceException
